                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94/2172: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Consul at Geneva</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Gilbert</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-10-16T18:00:00+01:00"
                            >October 16, 1931—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received October 16—1:25 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>209. Consulate’s 208, October 16, 6 [<hi rend="italic">5</hi>] p.m. Council met
                    at 6 p.m. and I delivered statement. I understand that you are releasing in
                    Washington.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Gilbert</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
